<i># Well, I love schooners
And I love ships #</i>

36:53.250 --> 36:56.750
<i># And I love that boat that tugs #</i>

36:56.833 --> 37:00.458
<i># I have nautical images #</i>

37:00.542 --> 37:03.083
<i># On all my sheets and rugs #</i>

37:03.167 --> 37:04.208
See what I did?

37:04.292 --> 37:07.583
<i># I, I, I #</i>

37:07.667 --> 37:10.958
<i># I love the sea #</i>

